channel.title: CVE Feed for Hewlett Packard Enterprise (HPE) -- EdgeConnect SD-WAN Orchestrator
channel.description: The latest CVEs for Hewlett Packard Enterprise (HPE) -- EdgeConnect SD-WAN Orchestrator

item.title: CVE-2023-37435|2024-10-04T15:51:02.673Z -- hewlett%20packard%20enterprise%20%28hpe%29 -- edgeconnect%20sd-wan%20orchestrator
item.description: Multiple vulnerabilities in the web-based management interface of EdgeConnect SD-WAN Orchestrator could allow an authenticated remote attacker to conduct SQL injection attacks against the EdgeConnect SD-WAN Orchestrator instance. An attacker could exploit these vulnerabilities to obtain and modify sensitive information in the underlying database potentially leading to the exposure and corruption of sensitive data controlled by the EdgeConnect SD-WAN Orchestrator host.
